00:42:56,380 --> 00:42:57,780
[SPEAKER_00] pa će biti 30 godina

929
00:42:57,780 --> 00:43:00,340
[SPEAKER_00] ti procesi izloženi.

930
00:43:00,340 --> 00:43:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatska ima tu jednu prednost,

931
00:43:02,519 --> 00:43:04,639
[SPEAKER_00] veliku, veliku, veliku prednost,

932
00:43:04,639 --> 00:43:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] jer je ona isto dobno

933
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] srednjoevropska i mediteranska sredozemna zemlja.

934
00:43:13,119 --> 00:43:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] Nijedna druge nemaju Europe.

935
00:43:14,659 --> 00:43:16,679
[SPEAKER_00] Na tom prostoru,

936
00:43:16,679 --> 00:43:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] te četvrte graditacijske stočke Evrope,

937
00:43:19,599 --> 00:43:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] u strateškom smislu,

938
00:43:20,960 --> 00:43:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] su sve te tri elipse moći,

939
00:43:24,920 --> 00:43:25,800
[SPEAKER_00] ova tri tabora,

940
00:43:25,800 --> 00:43:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] se presjecaju.

941
00:43:26,659 --> 00:43:27,559
[SPEAKER_00] To je već,

942
00:43:27,559 --> 00:43:28,820
[SPEAKER_00] idemo u teoriju skupova.

943
00:43:28,820 --> 00:43:31,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, presjecište tri skupaje kod nas.

944
00:43:31,760 --> 00:43:34,659
[SPEAKER_00] To je atlantizam ili geopolitika,

945
00:43:34,659 --> 00:43:36,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali sa sonaca toši i amerikanaca.

946
00:43:36,639 --> 00:43:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je kontinimalizam Rusije

947
00:43:39,199 --> 00:43:41,360
[SPEAKER_00] i njihove geopolitike.

948
00:43:41,360 --> 00:43:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] I to je kineske geopolitike,

949
00:43:43,519 --> 00:43:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] teolokracije ili Novog puta svile.

950
00:43:45,639 --> 00:43:47,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, naša politika,

951
00:43:47,699 --> 00:43:49,260
[SPEAKER_00] da je razumna,

952
00:43:49,260 --> 00:43:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] trebala je voditi politiku

953
00:43:50,659 --> 00:43:53,739
[SPEAKER_00] koju je imao Dubrovačka republika.

954
00:43:53,739 --> 00:43:56,239
[SPEAKER_00] I ona je bila na rastestu

955
00:43:56,239 --> 00:43:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] ondašnjih velesila

956
00:43:58,119 --> 00:44:01,139
[SPEAKER_00] i svidio kako je 600 godina

957
00:44:01,139 --> 00:44:03,639
[SPEAKER_00] opstala i toliko podarila

958
00:44:03,639 --> 00:44:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo nama Hrvatima,

959
00:44:05,579 --> 00:44:06,659
[SPEAKER_00] u svakome smislu

960
00:44:06,659 --> 00:44:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] od državotvorstva,

961
00:44:08,119 --> 00:44:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] upravljanja,

962
00:44:09,019 --> 00:44:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] gospodarske moći itd.

963
00:44:12,079 --> 00:44:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] Iako nije imala silu,

964
00:44:14,380 --> 00:44:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] ali je imala mudrost.

965
00:44:15,539 --> 00:44:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite kako se to sve može igrati.

966
00:44:17,900 --> 00:44:21,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se ti osvijestiš ono sve,

967
00:44:21,360 --> 00:44:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] osvijestiš svoj identitet.

968
00:44:23,000 --> 00:44:25,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je naš verbi problem?

969
00:44:25,980 --> 00:44:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] Što mi nismo osvijestili svoj identitet.

970
00:44:27,980 --> 00:44:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] I zato sam ja napisao knjigu

971
00:44:29,960 --> 00:44:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] uzvišena civilizacija.

972
00:44:31,199 --> 00:44:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jer naš intet je uništen

973
00:44:32,960 --> 00:44:34,400
[SPEAKER_00] onoga trenutka kada nije

974
00:44:34,400 --> 00:44:35,780
[SPEAKER_00] okultna oligarhija,

975
00:44:35,780 --> 00:44:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] germanska, njemačka,

976
00:44:37,659 --> 00:44:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] točnije,

977
00:44:38,239 --> 00:44:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] Hasbugovci,

978
00:44:39,380 --> 00:44:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] uvalili nekakve nepostojeće

979
00:44:41,840 --> 00:44:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] slovene

980
00:44:42,380 --> 00:44:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] da se doseli

981
00:44:43,460 --> 00:44:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] u nekakvom 6.

982
00:44:44,579 --> 00:44:45,719
[SPEAKER_00] 7. stoljeću.

983
00:44:45,719 --> 00:44:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] A to je znanost dokazala

984
00:44:47,500 --> 00:44:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] da nikakvi veliki seoba

985
00:44:48,840 --> 00:44:49,760
[SPEAKER_00] nije tamo bile.

986
00:44:49,760 --> 00:44:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, mi moramo

987
00:44:50,420 --> 00:44:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] prvo svijesti naš intet.

988
00:44:51,559 --> 00:44:52,780
[SPEAKER_00] Zato sam ja napisao tu knjigu.

989
00:44:52,780 --> 00:44:53,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

990
00:44:53,900 --> 00:44:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] sada su vremena,

991
00:44:55,480 --> 00:44:57,780
[SPEAKER_00] sasvim imamo mogućnosti,

992
00:44:57,840 --> 00:44:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] ješte tu svjećište.

993
00:44:59,159 --> 00:45:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] I naša razumna politika

994
00:45:00,940 --> 00:45:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] ne možemo mi mijenjati.

995
00:45:02,119 --> 00:45:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] Mi moramo uzeti

996
00:45:03,039 --> 00:45:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] datost koja je.

997
00:45:04,079 --> 00:45:05,239
[SPEAKER_00] A datost je

998
00:45:05,239 --> 00:45:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] da smo mi u NATO

999
00:45:06,079 --> 00:45:06,719
[SPEAKER_00] i da smo mi

1000
00:45:06,719 --> 00:45:08,079
[SPEAKER_00] članice EU.

1001
00:45:08,079 --> 00:45:10,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vremena će pokazati

1002
00:45:10,639 --> 00:45:11,679
[SPEAKER_00] ništa nije vječno

1003
00:45:11,679 --> 00:45:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] i da će se i NATO

1004
00:45:12,800 --> 00:45:14,239
[SPEAKER_00] i EU raspasti.

1005
00:45:14,239 --> 00:45:14,860
[SPEAKER_00] A što onda?

1006
00:45:15,019 --> 00:45:15,780
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujete u to?

1007
00:45:15,780 --> 00:45:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne, to je uvijek.

1008
00:45:17,059 --> 00:45:17,860
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako.

1009
00:45:17,860 --> 00:45:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] To ne bih kao...

1010
00:45:18,960 --> 00:45:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem na onoga razapeta,

1011
00:45:21,159 --> 00:45:22,320
[SPEAKER_00] u Golgosko pobjednika.

1012
00:45:22,320 --> 00:45:23,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ja u toga vjerujem.

1013
00:45:23,219 --> 00:45:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje, ja govorim kao strateg.

1014
00:45:25,760 --> 00:45:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ćemo poći

1015
00:45:26,900 --> 00:45:28,579
[SPEAKER_00] od te mudrosti životna,

1016
00:45:28,579 --> 00:45:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] da ništa nije vječno

1017
00:45:30,199 --> 00:45:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] i da ima svoje rađanje,

1018
00:45:32,579 --> 00:45:33,579
[SPEAKER_00] svoje rast

1019
00:45:33,579 --> 00:45:34,579
[SPEAKER_00] i svoje umiranje.

1020
00:45:34,579 --> 00:45:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] E tako i to.

1021
00:45:35,340 --> 00:45:37,280
[SPEAKER_00] On je nastao,

1022
00:45:37,280 --> 00:45:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] NATO je nastao

1023
00:45:38,599 --> 00:45:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] nakon drugosvjetskog rata

1024
00:45:40,019 --> 00:45:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] i uspostave bipolarne podjele svijeta.

1025
00:45:43,239 --> 00:45:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je meni jasno,

1026
00:45:44,559 --> 00:45:46,260
[SPEAKER_00] već koliko 30 godina

1027
00:45:46,260 --> 00:45:48,219
[SPEAKER_00] bipolarne podjele svijeta nema.

1028
00:45:48,219 --> 00:45:50,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ali NATO još ima.

1029
00:45:50,059 --> 00:45:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] A sada ima jednopolarni svijet.

1030
00:45:52,960 --> 00:45:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] On se sada ruši.

1031
00:45:54,380 --> 00:45:56,360
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome nastaje

1032
00:45:56,360 --> 00:45:58,059
[SPEAKER_00] višepolarnost svijeta,

1033
00:45:58,059 --> 00:46:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] a u višepolarnosti svijeta

1034
00:46:00,019 --> 00:46:01,980
[SPEAKER_00] postavaju ono što je bilo preko

1035
00:46:01,980 --> 00:46:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] prije mora nestati.

1036
00:46:03,619 --> 00:46:05,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jer se će sve transformirati.

1037
00:46:05,519 --> 00:46:08,300
[SPEAKER_01] Admirale, da vas pitam sad.

1038
00:46:08,300 --> 00:46:09,579
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ste malo prije spomenuli

1039
00:46:09,579 --> 00:46:10,340
[SPEAKER_01] Vis Baden.

1040
00:46:10,340 --> 00:46:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oko toga se koplja lome

1041
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] i to je jedno popularno odredište

1042
00:46:14,119 --> 00:46:16,300
[SPEAKER_01] za hrvatske političare

1043
00:46:16,300 --> 00:46:17,659
[SPEAKER_01] koji vole reći

1044
00:46:17,659 --> 00:46:18,800
[SPEAKER_01] da tamo nam je mjesto

1045
00:46:18,800 --> 00:46:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] ili ne tamo našim vojnicima nije mjesto.

1046
00:46:21,000 --> 00:46:23,500
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko je po vama moguće

1047
00:46:23,500 --> 00:46:26,199
[SPEAKER_01] da se razvije na evropskom tlu

1048
00:46:26,199 --> 00:46:28,119
[SPEAKER_01] dvostruka linija zapovjedenja

1049
00:46:28,119 --> 00:46:29,780
[SPEAKER_01] vezana uz Rusko?

1050
00:46:29,780 --> 00:46:30,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako.

1051
00:46:30,699 --> 00:46:32,099
[SPEAKER_00] Inače, kad govorimo

1052
00:46:32,099 --> 00:46:33,900
[SPEAKER_00] o dvostrukoj liniji zapovjedenja,

1053
00:46:33,900 --> 00:46:35,480
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno, Hrvati bi rekli

1054
00:46:35,480 --> 00:46:37,400
[SPEAKER_00] crti, iako je linija istoj Hrvatskoj.

1055
00:46:37,480 --> 00:46:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] srta nije malo šale, moramo i mi razmeti

1056
00:46:39,960 --> 00:46:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj ovako.

1057
00:46:41,400 --> 00:46:44,039
[SPEAKER_01] Pa neće da slada ovi sada jezičari

1058
00:46:44,039 --> 00:46:44,860
[SPEAKER_01] jer zbog toga...

1059
00:46:44,860 --> 00:46:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo neko rade što god hoće,

1060
00:46:46,599 --> 00:46:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] jer moramo mi gajiti

1061
00:46:48,139 --> 00:46:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] naš Hrvatski prekrasni jezik

1062
00:46:50,019 --> 00:46:50,719
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje.

1063
00:46:51,679 --> 00:46:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] sve uzeti druge i dobro je linija,

1064
00:46:53,940 --> 00:46:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] jer ima negdje gdje možeš uporaviti crto,

1065
00:46:56,079 --> 00:46:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne možeš uporaviti...

1066
00:46:58,239 --> 00:46:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] bolje uporaviti liniju.

1067
00:46:59,900 --> 00:47:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, pa sve je to u redu,

1068
00:47:01,880 --> 00:47:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] jedno i drugo je dobro došlo.

1069
00:47:03,139 --> 00:47:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ne spijemo biti s tim uptereseni.

1070
00:47:05,880 --> 00:47:07,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa, bogatstvo Hrvatskog jezika

1071
00:47:07,300 --> 00:47:07,940
[SPEAKER_01] iznad svega.

1072
00:47:07,940 --> 00:47:08,840
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, tako je.

1073
00:47:08,840 --> 00:47:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] Bogatstvo, stvarno je Hrvatski jezik

1074
00:47:11,619 --> 00:47:13,699
[SPEAKER_00] bogat u mnogim elementima.

1075
00:47:13,699 --> 00:47:17,139
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo sada na ovo pitanje...

1076
00:47:17,960 --> 00:47:19,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dvostruka crta ili dvostruka linija.

1077
00:47:19,699 --> 00:47:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, dvostruka crta je izmišljena

1078
00:47:21,380 --> 00:47:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] samo za nas Hrvate,

1079
00:47:22,480 --> 00:47:24,219
[SPEAKER_00] kao što je izmišljena

1080
00:47:24,219 --> 00:47:26,179
[SPEAKER_00] preko mjerno granatiranje.

1081
00:47:26,179 --> 00:47:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde sad.

1082
00:47:27,639 --> 00:47:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ja zavodio.

1083
00:47:30,059 --> 00:47:32,739
[SPEAKER_00] U našoj operaciji Olujer,

1084
00:47:32,739 --> 00:47:34,480
[SPEAKER_00] u napadu na Knin,

1085
00:47:34,480 --> 00:47:36,699
[SPEAKER_00] topično-raketne snage

1086
00:47:36,699 --> 00:47:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] gađale su šest ciljeva.

1087
00:47:39,900 --> 00:47:41,320
[SPEAKER_00] Nabranje ih.

1088
00:47:41,320 --> 00:47:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna vojarna, druga vojarna,

1089
00:47:43,380 --> 00:47:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] treća vojarna,

1090
00:47:44,360 --> 00:47:46,300
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno zgrada,

1091
00:47:46,559 --> 00:47:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] granaštaba vojske srpske krajine,

1092
00:47:48,880 --> 00:47:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] rezultencija predsjednika Martića

1093
00:47:51,199 --> 00:47:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] i glavno Raskriži u Kninu.

1094
00:47:52,739 --> 00:47:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, svi šeste su vojni ciljere.

1095
00:47:55,739 --> 00:47:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ispaljeno po srskim izvješćima,

1096
00:47:59,460 --> 00:48:00,719
[SPEAKER_00] gdje smo iskilili,

1097
00:48:00,719 --> 00:48:01,900
[SPEAKER_00] ja se ovdje u vojnovojstvu službu,

1098
00:48:01,900 --> 00:48:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] u Beograd i Banja Luku,

1099
00:48:04,000 --> 00:48:08,699
[SPEAKER_00] gdje piše šef vojno-obraštane službe

1100
00:48:08,699 --> 00:48:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] te vojske, te pseudovojske,

1101
00:48:10,619 --> 00:48:12,639
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, nazovimo to uvjetno

1102
00:48:12,639 --> 00:48:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] moj kolega sa druge strane,

1103
00:48:15,159 --> 00:48:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] svom kolegi,

1104
00:48:16,219 --> 00:48:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] načelniku oboještene uprave u Beogradu,

1105
00:48:19,980 --> 00:48:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] da su Hrvati ispalili,

1106
00:48:24,079 --> 00:48:25,360
[SPEAKER_00] sve slušajte,

1107
00:48:25,360 --> 00:48:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] 250 do 300 projektila rašto kalibra

1108
00:48:29,159 --> 00:48:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] i da su gađali ovi šest siljeva.

1109
00:48:31,679 --> 00:48:32,940
[SPEAKER_00] To oni su povijek na brojni.

1110
00:48:32,940 --> 00:48:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže, mora se priznati da su pogodili

1111
00:48:36,260 --> 00:48:39,260
[SPEAKER_00] i ovo generalna štab.

1112
00:48:39,260 --> 00:48:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, mora da je tamo neki dobar artiljerac,

1113
00:48:43,880 --> 00:48:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] kad je tako mogao ubaciti to.

1114
00:48:46,320 --> 00:48:49,699
[SPEAKER_00] A to je ubacio, su bile besplote letali sa povijedanje

1115
00:48:49,699 --> 00:48:51,280
[SPEAKER_00] i možeš odmah korekciju da me govori.

1116
00:48:51,280 --> 00:48:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] Notabene, na Hrvatskom sudju se je dokazalo

1117
00:48:56,340 --> 00:48:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] da je samo u Gorjom knjinu,

1118
00:48:59,420 --> 00:49:00,860
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno točnije u Golubiću,

1119
00:49:00,860 --> 00:49:03,360
[SPEAKER_00] nastradao samo jedan civil i to vjerojatno,

1120
00:49:03,360 --> 00:49:04,760
[SPEAKER_00] ne od nikakvog djelovanja,

1121
00:49:04,760 --> 00:49:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] vjerojatno ispao iz ovoga traktora što su oni išli,

1122
00:49:07,599 --> 00:49:08,900
[SPEAKER_00] nešto slično se da godin.

1123
00:49:09,440 --> 00:49:13,719
[SPEAKER_00] I sada usporedite to ovoj što se događa u Gazi

1124
00:49:13,719 --> 00:49:15,840
[SPEAKER_00] ili što se događa u Beirutu, Libanonu.

1125
00:49:15,840 --> 00:49:20,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, izmišljenio je pojem prekomjernog granatiranja

1126
00:49:20,019 --> 00:49:23,079
[SPEAKER_00] da bi se naš general Gotovina i naš general Markač

1127
00:49:23,079 --> 00:49:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] proglasili ratnim zločinicima u Hagu.

1128
00:49:25,900 --> 00:49:26,980
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan pojem.

1129
00:49:26,980 --> 00:49:29,980
[SPEAKER_00] Onda sad tim ide topniški dnevnice.

1130
00:49:29,980 --> 00:49:34,820
[SPEAKER_00] Nikakva vojska nema topniške dnevnice.

1131
00:49:34,820 --> 00:49:38,260
[SPEAKER_00] E, sad tim je, da bi se to dokazalo,

1132
00:49:38,260 --> 00:49:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] inače to izmislio, tu crtu u slučaju Blaškića,

1133
00:49:41,539 --> 00:49:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] odvjetnik Anton Obilo.

1134
00:49:43,519 --> 00:49:46,780
[SPEAKER_00] Nema vojska dvostruku crtu.

1135
00:49:46,780 --> 00:49:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] Niti može imati jer je to čista kirarkija.

1136
00:49:49,039 --> 00:49:51,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ili imaš crtu ili je nemaš.

1137
00:49:51,820 --> 00:49:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zanimljivo je, kod te dvostruke crtve,

1138
00:49:56,019 --> 00:50:00,599
[SPEAKER_00] kod nas Hrvata, ta dvostruka, kriva crta,

1139
00:50:00,599 --> 00:50:03,940
[SPEAKER_00] bili bi ovako predsjednik Tuđva,

1140
00:50:03,940 --> 00:50:07,239
[SPEAKER_00] ministar Šušak, general Bobetkoj, sad mi i ostali.

1141
00:50:07,239 --> 00:50:10,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ali oni, to je po njima kriva crta,

1142
00:50:10,659 --> 00:50:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] ili ta dvostruka, a ta druga koja bi po njima bile prava,

1143
00:50:14,559 --> 00:50:15,880
[SPEAKER_00] nikad nisu definirali.

1144
00:50:15,880 --> 00:50:18,360
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nema.

1145
00:50:18,360 --> 00:50:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] U ovome slučaju je, slučaju,

1146
00:50:20,519 --> 00:50:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] vratimo se na ovom Vizbadenu.

1147
00:50:24,199 --> 00:50:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] To je, što je rekao naš predsjednik,

1148
00:50:26,900 --> 00:50:29,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zora Milanović, ispravno.

1149
00:50:29,099 --> 00:50:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] To je operativno za pojedništvo, za izvođenje druge etape rata zapada,

1150
00:50:36,420 --> 00:50:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] u ovome slučaju, Europe protiv Rusije.

1151
00:50:40,800 --> 00:50:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] I sada, u ovo zadnje vrijeme, bilo je zaokupljeno svim novim oružjem,

1152
00:50:48,139 --> 00:50:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] koja je lansirana od strane ruskih snaga,

1153
00:50:51,400 --> 00:50:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] a to je orešnik, ako mi kažemo, ruski ariješnik,

1154
00:50:55,820 --> 00:50:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] na Njepo-Petrovsk.

1155
00:50:58,860 --> 00:51:04,139
[SPEAKER_00] Točnije, na veliki proizvodni kapacitet.

1156
00:51:04,559 --> 00:51:08,159
[SPEAKER_00] Zove se Južmaš, gdje u vrijeme Sovjetskog savjeza

1157
00:51:08,159 --> 00:51:10,219
[SPEAKER_00] se proizvodili, između ostaloga,

1158
00:51:10,219 --> 00:51:13,179
[SPEAKER_00] rekatni motori iza svemirske letove,

1159
00:51:13,179 --> 00:51:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] naravno, iza rakete.

1160
00:51:14,500 --> 00:51:17,679
[SPEAKER_01] Rijepeno, kakve simbolike u tome?

1161
00:51:17,679 --> 00:51:19,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ima, ima, ima velike simbolike.

1162
00:51:19,760 --> 00:51:21,639
[SPEAKER_00] To ljudi ne znaju.

1163
00:51:21,639 --> 00:51:25,179
[SPEAKER_00] Njepo-Petrovsk, sada go oni zovu Dnjipro,

1164
00:51:25,179 --> 00:51:27,360
[SPEAKER_00] kao i rijeku, to je Dnjepro uvijek,

1165
00:51:27,360 --> 00:51:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, to nekako rade tako kao hoće.

1166
00:51:31,460 --> 00:51:34,059
[SPEAKER_00] A sama riječ govori Dnjepo-Petrovsk,

1167
00:51:34,059 --> 00:51:36,059
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, to je grad Petrov nad Dnjepro.

1168
00:51:36,059 --> 00:51:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, govori što je i koga je osnovio,

1169
00:51:38,659 --> 00:51:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, Petar Veliki.

1170
00:51:39,539 --> 00:51:40,260
[SPEAKER_00] Petar Veliki, da.

1171
00:51:40,260 --> 00:51:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] A zanimljivo z Dnjepo-Petrovska je u to,

1172
00:51:42,420 --> 00:51:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] što se tu nalazi najveća sinagoga na svijetu.

1173
00:51:45,420 --> 00:51:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] Inače, vrlo blizu Dnjepo-Petrovska

1174
00:51:50,619 --> 00:51:54,639
[SPEAKER_00] je bilo Hazarsko glavni grad,

1175
00:51:54,639 --> 00:51:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] nazovemo je, zvao se Itil.

1176
00:51:55,940 --> 00:51:58,679
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, od 8. do 10. stoljeća

1177
00:51:58,679 --> 00:52:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] tu je bila Hazarska država,

1178
00:52:00,380 --> 00:52:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] Hazarska država na čelu je bio

1179
00:52:03,559 --> 00:52:05,179
[SPEAKER_00] Kagan. Dakle, dalje,

1180
00:52:05,179 --> 00:52:07,559
[SPEAKER_00] odatle se, to su bio

1181
00:52:07,559 --> 00:52:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] turkijski narod koji je doselio

1182
00:52:09,380 --> 00:52:11,679
[SPEAKER_00] na ta područaj i koji je uzeo

1183
00:52:11,679 --> 00:52:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] hebrejsku vjeru.

1184
00:52:13,119 --> 00:52:15,460
[SPEAKER_00] To su ti velika većina

1185
00:52:15,460 --> 00:52:17,699
[SPEAKER_00] današnjih židova ili Hazara.

1186
00:52:17,699 --> 00:52:19,340
[SPEAKER_00] Oni sebe vole zvati

1187
00:52:19,340 --> 00:52:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] Aškenazima.

1188
00:52:20,159 --> 00:52:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] Da su oni potremci.

1189
00:52:21,179 --> 00:52:22,900
[SPEAKER_00] Oni nisu govorili

1190
00:52:22,900 --> 00:52:25,440
[SPEAKER_00] ni hebrejski, ni ti pisali hebrejski pismo.

1191
00:52:25,440 --> 00:52:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] Oni imaju svoje,

1192
00:52:26,119 --> 00:52:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] koje se zove Jidiš.

1193
00:52:28,099 --> 00:52:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] Jidiš može se dobro razumijeti.

1194
00:52:30,880 --> 00:52:33,239
[SPEAKER_00] Onaj ko govori staro-njemaški,

1195
00:52:33,239 --> 00:52:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] staro-germanski, jezki,

1196
00:52:34,519 --> 00:52:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] ima tu puno ovih naših burinskih riječi.

1197
00:52:37,360 --> 00:52:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, burini, mi smo potom

1198
00:52:38,599 --> 00:52:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] cilira, ne slaveni, a i zove burini.

1199
00:52:40,460 --> 00:52:42,300
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je to.

1200
00:52:42,460 --> 00:52:43,639
[SPEAKER_00] Moralo se razgovoriti.

1201
00:52:43,639 --> 00:52:45,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo što se događa u Ukrajini,

1202
00:52:45,199 --> 00:52:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] to je neki rat.

1203
00:52:45,960 --> 00:52:47,280
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je Hazarsku,

1204
00:52:47,280 --> 00:52:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] tu carstvo,

1205
00:52:48,000 --> 00:52:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] Razorija, jer se oni išli napasti

1206
00:52:51,199 --> 00:52:53,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kijevsku Rusiju.

1207
00:52:53,199 --> 00:52:55,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je središte ruskog zala se

1208
00:52:55,880 --> 00:52:56,699
[SPEAKER_00] Kijevska Rusija.

1209
00:52:56,699 --> 00:52:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] I u devetom stoljeću išli se napasti

1210
00:52:59,639 --> 00:53:01,920
[SPEAKER_00] i onda se oni Hazariju pobjedio.

1211
00:53:01,920 --> 00:53:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ruski knjez svjatovstvo prvi,

1212
00:53:04,579 --> 00:53:06,440
[SPEAKER_00] a potpuno je rasturio.

1213
00:53:06,440 --> 00:53:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] To je Vladimir Veliki.

1214
00:53:07,519 --> 00:53:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] Zato se on zove Vladimir Veliki.

1215
00:53:09,079 --> 00:53:10,679
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je toliko

1216
00:53:10,679 --> 00:53:14,219
[SPEAKER_00] popularno ime Vladimir

1217
00:53:14,219 --> 00:53:15,739
[SPEAKER_00] kod Rusa.

1218
00:53:15,739 --> 00:53:17,659
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo, i danas su protagonisti

1219
00:53:17,659 --> 00:53:19,300
[SPEAKER_00] u Ukrajini dvoja Vladimira.

1220
00:53:19,300 --> 00:53:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] Da, pa ćeš nećiš.

1221
00:53:20,900 --> 00:53:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] Sve dođe na vladu.

1222
00:53:22,159 --> 00:53:23,820
[SPEAKER_01] A u Hrvatskoj na šeksa.

1223
00:53:23,820 --> 00:53:24,559
[SPEAKER_00] Molim.

1224
00:53:24,559 --> 00:53:25,780
[SPEAKER_01] A u Hrvatskoj na šeksa.

1225
00:53:25,780 --> 00:53:26,780
[SPEAKER_00] A u Hrvatskoj na šeksa.

1226
00:53:26,780 --> 00:53:27,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kod nas on sve ima.

1227
00:53:27,800 --> 00:53:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] On to radi i oblači.

1228
00:53:29,340 --> 00:53:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to su

1229
00:53:30,579 --> 00:53:32,840
[SPEAKER_00] sada ti događe.

1230
00:53:32,840 --> 00:53:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] Vracimo se ome za pojednišću.

1231
00:53:34,320 --> 00:53:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] Sve to važno.

1232
00:53:35,159 --> 00:53:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pravno.

1233
00:53:36,000 --> 00:53:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] I kada je lansiran rešnik,

1234
00:53:38,900 --> 00:53:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] onda je opet, opet.

1235
00:53:40,880 --> 00:53:42,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kod nas ne zove onaj ko zna.

1236
00:53:42,519 --> 00:53:44,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ko zna.

1237
00:53:44,400 --> 00:53:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] Njega ne zove da uprotumači.

1238
00:53:45,920 --> 00:53:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, ja sam nakon završetka

1239
00:53:47,980 --> 00:53:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] Vojne akademije,

1240
00:53:48,880 --> 00:53:51,260
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno fakulteta

1241
00:53:51,260 --> 00:53:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] Vojno-Pomorskoga,

1242
00:53:52,460 --> 00:53:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] imao specializaciju

1243
00:53:54,380 --> 00:53:56,039
[SPEAKER_00] između ostaloga

1244
00:53:56,039 --> 00:53:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] borba protipanetnih raketa

1245
00:53:58,699 --> 00:53:59,800
[SPEAKER_00] i borba protipodmorca.

1246
00:54:00,019 --> 00:54:01,739
[SPEAKER_00] govorim od onašeg vremena.

1247
00:54:01,739 --> 00:54:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] Nije to istog.

1248
00:54:02,519 --> 00:54:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] Danas je to normo otišlo.

1249
00:54:04,920 --> 00:54:07,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mogu te tragove pratiti.

1250
00:54:07,159 --> 00:54:08,719
[SPEAKER_00] To je jednostavno tako.

1251
00:54:08,719 --> 00:54:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kako imate specializaciju,

1252
00:54:09,960 --> 00:54:10,780
[SPEAKER_00] možete vrlo brzo

1253
00:54:10,780 --> 00:54:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] i nove stvari naučiti.

1254
00:54:12,940 --> 00:54:14,360
[SPEAKER_01] Znate što je unutarnja,

1255
00:54:14,360 --> 00:54:16,300
[SPEAKER_00] što je vanjski strategijski krug.

1256
00:54:16,300 --> 00:54:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] I sada ovi ostali,

1257
00:54:19,119 --> 00:54:22,199
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda je to bila raketa

1258
00:54:22,199 --> 00:54:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] RS-27 rubež,

1259
00:54:25,039 --> 00:54:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] rubež je inače granica u ruskom,

1260
00:54:27,400 --> 00:54:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] rubež, rub.

1261
00:54:28,480 --> 00:54:30,739
[SPEAKER_00] To je granica u ruskom jesku.

1262
00:54:30,739 --> 00:54:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda je, nije,

1263
00:54:32,500 --> 00:54:33,800
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda ne znamo,

1264
00:54:33,800 --> 00:54:35,360
[SPEAKER_00] rješnik zašto je on,

1265
00:54:35,360 --> 00:54:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] pa je li to.

1266
00:54:36,199 --> 00:54:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje jednostavno ovako.

1267
00:54:37,460 --> 00:54:41,179
[SPEAKER_00] Rusi, budući da su dosegli

1268
00:54:41,179 --> 00:54:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] vladanjem

1269
00:54:42,500 --> 00:54:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] hiperzvučne,

1270
00:54:44,019 --> 00:54:45,719
[SPEAKER_00] hipersofnične tehnologije,

1271
00:54:46,300 --> 00:54:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] oni imaju mnoge rakete

1272
00:54:49,559 --> 00:54:51,880
[SPEAKER_00] koje su još iz vremena

1273
00:54:51,880 --> 00:54:52,820
[SPEAKER_00] Sovjetskog savjeza.

1274
00:54:52,820 --> 00:54:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] Neke su napustili,

1275
00:54:54,199 --> 00:54:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] neke poboljšali.

1276
00:54:55,079 --> 00:54:57,400
[SPEAKER_00] I te su rakete nosači,

1277
00:54:57,400 --> 00:54:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] nositelji.

1278
00:54:58,380 --> 00:55:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] I naravno da je ta raketa,

1279
00:55:01,960 --> 00:55:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] recimo Pandan,

1280
00:55:03,960 --> 00:55:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] te rakete RS-26

1281
00:55:05,960 --> 00:55:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] je američki Pershing.

1282
00:55:07,500 --> 00:55:09,179
[SPEAKER_00] To se definira

1283
00:55:09,179 --> 00:55:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] u ovim sporozima

1284
00:55:10,199 --> 00:55:11,360
[SPEAKER_00] o nuklearnom oružju

1285
00:55:11,360 --> 00:55:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] kao rakete srednjeg dometa

1286
00:55:13,460 --> 00:55:14,059
[SPEAKER_00] i jesu.

1287
00:55:14,059 --> 00:55:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] Rakete srednjega dometa

1288
00:55:16,219 --> 00:55:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] su do 5,5 tisuća kilometara.

1289
00:55:18,980 --> 00:55:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] Iznad toga

1290
00:55:20,860 --> 00:55:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] su rakete

1291
00:55:23,380 --> 00:55:24,579
[SPEAKER_00] strateške namjene.

1292
00:55:24,579 --> 00:55:27,699
[SPEAKER_00] Jedne i druge

1293
00:55:27,699 --> 00:55:29,019
[SPEAKER_00] su balističke rakete.

1294
00:55:29,019 --> 00:55:30,300
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, lete je po nekom

1295
00:55:30,300 --> 00:55:31,920
[SPEAKER_00] krivulju ovako otprilike.

1296
00:55:31,920 --> 00:55:34,219
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, približno nekakva parabola,

1297
00:55:34,219 --> 00:55:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] nije čista parabola,

1298
00:55:35,500 --> 00:55:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] nisu im ovi krakovi isti,

1299
00:55:37,619 --> 00:55:39,260
[SPEAKER_00] ali slišno može.

1300
00:55:39,260 --> 00:55:39,760
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, rako.

1301
00:55:39,760 --> 00:55:41,199
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, pokazujem ruku.

1302
00:55:42,480 --> 00:55:42,840
[SPEAKER_00] sada,

1303
00:55:42,840 --> 00:55:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] ova raketa koja nosi

1304
00:55:45,059 --> 00:55:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] neku bojevu glavu,

1305
00:55:46,380 --> 00:55:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] grećemo bojevom glave,

1306
00:55:47,440 --> 00:55:49,440
[SPEAKER_00] ona, kada se lansira,

1307
00:55:49,440 --> 00:55:51,159
[SPEAKER_00] ona se diže

1308
00:55:51,159 --> 00:55:52,079
[SPEAKER_00] gore,

1309
00:55:52,079 --> 00:55:53,739
[SPEAKER_00] dođe u vršnu točku

1310
00:55:53,739 --> 00:55:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] i ota se spušta

1311
00:55:55,119 --> 00:55:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] prema cilju

1312
00:55:55,820 --> 00:55:56,840
[SPEAKER_00] koji je programiran,

1313
00:55:56,840 --> 00:55:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] taj cilj.

1314
00:55:57,420 --> 00:56:01,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ona, u vršnu točku,

1315
00:56:01,320 --> 00:56:02,739
[SPEAKER_00] završava svoju misiju,

1316
00:56:02,739 --> 00:56:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] tada se otvara

1317
00:56:04,400 --> 00:56:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] ta bojeva glava

1318
00:56:05,579 --> 00:56:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] i iz nje izlaze

1319
00:56:07,619 --> 00:56:09,719
[SPEAKER_00] 1, 2, 3, pa 12,

1320
00:56:09,719 --> 00:56:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] u nekim čak

1321
00:56:10,539 --> 00:56:12,400
[SPEAKER_00] može izići i 15

1322
00:56:12,400 --> 00:56:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] modula,

1323
00:56:14,420 --> 00:56:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno blokova

1324
00:56:17,840 --> 00:56:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] u kojima ima

1325
00:56:20,539 --> 00:56:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] eksploziv ili nešto drugo.

1326
00:56:22,099 --> 00:56:23,079
[SPEAKER_00] smo se sad razumijeli,

1327
00:56:23,079 --> 00:56:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] protiraketni sustavi,

1328
00:56:25,699 --> 00:56:27,599
[SPEAKER_00] najosjetljiviji

1329
00:56:27,599 --> 00:56:29,760
